Package: basinPhysiografics
Title: Physiographic characteristics of watershed basins
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Arthur", "Calegario", , "tcalegario@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1921-5234")))
Description: The basinPhysiographics package was developed to compile functions
         aimed at obtaining the physiographic characteristics watershed basins. Currently,
         the package assists users in obtaining digital elevation model (DEM) subproducts and
         delineating watershed basins.
